data.description: You'll enjoy the amount of space you'll find inside this custom-built home. The Master is on the main level along with an additional bedroom and bath, a formal Dining Room, Living Room, Kitchen, Breakfast area and family Den/Sun porch. The finished basement boasts enough space for workout rooms, game rooms, and media areas. You'll have a total of 5 Bedrooms/3Baths on the upper two floors. Finishes include Stainless appliances, Ceramic tile, Hardwood, Granite Kitchen Counters, Plantation shutters and beautiful T&G wood in the Den. In addition, there is walk-in attic storage. The main and 2nd floor HVAC units are new and the other 2 units are approx. 10 years old. From this City West home, Chattanooga and Atlanta are only a short drive away.
